| Data Type     | Description                              | Example Values           |
| ------------- | ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------ |
| `CHAR(n)`     | Fixed-length string                      | `'abc   '`               |
| `VARCHAR(n)`  | Variable-length string                   | `'hello'`                |
| `TEXT`        | Large text                               | `'This is a long note.'` |
| `NCHAR(n)`    | Fixed-length Unicode string (SQL Server) | `'abc'`                  |
| `NVARCHAR(n)` | Variable-length Unicode string           | `'नमस्ते'`               |
